primary.context: Caller wants to know when their reservation at Vacation Village at Weston is scheduled.
primary.detail: The agent correctly identified that reservations are out of scope and transferred the caller to the concierge department.

steps: Agent offered transfer to concierge or owner services.
Caller selected concierge and was transferred.

clarifications.note: Agent asked if caller was still there after silence.

actions.detail: Agent captured caller name David Rowan.
Transferred to concierge department for reservation help.

insights.summary: The caller wanted to check reservation dates, which is an out-of-scope task. The agent verified the caller's name and successfully transferred them to the concierge department.
insights.verbatim: I'm checking to see when my reservation is for Vacation Village at Weston.
